{"tid":1628487,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"冬季流感高峰期提早來臨 呼籲大家出街戴口罩","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:48:10.000Z","uid":11485,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"974223002c5c3864ec19244358afff776ebd7a14","tid":1628487,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"《港大學者預計本港今年冬季流感高峰期提早來臨》（香港電台）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482296-20190924.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482296-20190924.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfENjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=5f2c34a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482296-20190924.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=50ae7c9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482296-20190924.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n「港大醫學院內科學系傳染病科主任及助理院長孔繁毅表示，以往流感高峰期通常在12月底開始，但本周已有病人因甲型流感入院留醫，因此估計冬季流感高峰期將會提早來臨，甚至可能持續到明年2月左右 &hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n根據衛生署衛生防護中心有關「季節性流行性感冒」嘅健康資訊，健康嘅人患上季節性流感後，病徵可包括<ins>發燒、咳嗽、喉嚨痛、流鼻水、肌肉痛、疲倦、頭痛、嘔吐同腹瀉</ins>等。免疫力較低嘅人士一旦染上流感，可以係嚴重嘅疾病，並且<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>可能會出現支氣管炎或肺炎等併發症，甚至死亡</ins></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我在此呼籲各位巴絲，保護自己同家人，出街記得佩戴口罩。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4915f93d50f686a57ba616d5881b10df02038b9d","tid":1628487,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:18:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3e66df8d89f84ad6e61a770e04670514dd95b10","tid":1628487,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f76e18321d55ceaad50019802f789c01d7eb0a1c","tid":1628487,"uid":18001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:36:15.0